text: Umerkot is a town in Sindh, Pakistan. Umerkot may also refer to: *Umerkot District, an administrative unit of Sindh, Pakistan *Umerkot Fort, a fort in Pakistan ==See also== *Umerkote, a town in Odissa, India *Umerkote (Odisha Vidhan Sabha constituency), a constituency of Nabarangpur district, India *
title: Umerkot (disambiguation)
